data.description: This Lenar two-story home is a charming haven with three bedrooms and two and a half baths, providing a perfect balance of space and comfort. The full kitchen seamlessly connects to the dining area and living room, creating a welcoming atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The upstairs loft adds an element of versatility, serving as a cozy retreat or functional workspace. The private patio adjoining the loft is a delightful touch, offering a serene outdoor space to relax and enjoy moments of tranquility. With thoughtful design and modern amenities, your Lenar home embodies both practicality and style, making it a haven for daily living. Close to all your needs.
